result.name: Joy Hing Roasted Meat

reviews.text: We ordered take away the first night we arrived.  Even though it was late we enjoyed moist pork belly and bbq pork.  Comes with veg, rice and soup.  Good value.  Very tasty. And very friendly service.

This is one of THE bedrock traditional Hong Kong roast culinary restaurant which has been in business for a very very long time.

Come for the food, not for the decor, crowds and environment.

You will not be disappointed with their roast meats, which is also very reasonably priced. This is what authentic Hong Kong Cantonese soul food means.

Amazingly efficient operation. Don't come for the service, come for the food and the old school HK experience. Head in and they'll probably seat you at a shared tabled. Went for the 叉燒飯 (barbecued pork rice), which came less than a minute after I was seated. The squeeze bottle on the table is the jus from roasting the meats, which you should shoot all over the rice. Pay at the register on the way out.
Poor service, unethical, they gave you one price for the dish, but charged other table lower price for the same dish. Seats are very uncomfortable and plates are dirty.

Was the best HK-style BBQ in town when I first visited in around 2005. However, food quality is dropping much after a decade. The price did raise a bit but is still very reasonable. Do not expect the hygiene level to be high.

result.name: 再興燒臘店

reviews.text: 香港最好嘅燒味👍🏻
叉燒出色👍

埋單收錯錢 仲要窒你。呢間餐廳燒味叫幾好，餐廳舊價錢平 你當然唔會要求有服務。我食咁多次，食完就快趣俾錢走，次次都相安無事。   

今日明明無乜人，唔知乜原因個啊姐下下都
 Hi 埋黎，我覺得好似俾人抽緊水。隻腳又俾佢啲職員踩到。

見到佢而家收八達通，咁我就埋單($50)，佢收我張單 講話$205 (外賣客) , 我當然同佢講返。 
佢：淨係做你一個人生意就死。
我照拍咭，個短髮女人 咪又係要退返現金俾我。

完全係貼錢買難受，我以後都唔撚去。
口味偏淡沒香氣，鵝肉偏乾 燒肉並不是五花腩部位燒的，不知道是他沒五花燒腩還是他的燒肉就是大燒豬，所以吃起來在口感味道上就沒一般燒臘店的燒肉來的香，口味算是普通，加上米飯選擇的是舊米 米的品質也有點差，味道跟口感確實是我在香港吃過當中算是比較差的，以有店面的燒臘店來說，價錢算是便宜的
